@WHOWPRO @WHOSEARO @WHO_Europe @pahowho @WHOEMRO @WHOAFRO Q: Does the new #coronavirus (2019-nC0V) affect older people, or are younger people also susceptible?
A: People of all ages can be infected by the virus.
Older people &amp; those with pre-existing medical conditions appear to be more vulnerable to becoming severely ill with the virus https://t.co/6C5QFuiI13
